of  publicity  about  a  former  NASA  astronaut.  I  watched  that,  and 
one  of  the  things  that  I  admired  is  other  NASA  astronauts  came 
and  spoke  publicly  and  said,  ‘‘We  worry  about  the  human  being 
here.’’  But  having  mentioned  that,  is  there  anything  in  that  cir-
cumstance,  or  anything  with  respect  to  what  you  saw  and  heard, 

