Dr.  GRIFFIN.  Well,  sir,  that  is  exactly  what  we  are  looking  at. 
The allegations against Captain Nowak are, of course, very serious. 
It’s  a  legal  matter.  It’s  in  the  legal  system.  I  just  will  not  address 
those  allegations.  But  clearly  she  is  in  major  trouble,  and  clearly 
we  failed,  as  an  institution,  to  recognize  that  she  was  very  trou-
